  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wanted criminal was last seen in the city where your residence is located. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, you heard someone broke into your house... Could it be him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're being trapped in your bathroom, <strong>be quiet</strong> and find a way to save yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please Use headphones for the Best Experience</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It is a point-and-click short puzzle game</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Search through the room and find useful items, figure out puzzles to save yourself</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You need to hear anything outside the room to know if the criminal is nearby before your action</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~ 30 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This Game may contain possible depictions or elements of violence</strong></p></li></ul>",
